---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const base = '/tradfi-onchain';
---

<Layout title="TradFi × Onchain">
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pt-24 pb-16">
    <p class="text-cyan-400 text-sm font-medium tracking-wider uppercase mb-4">
      <span class="lang-en">For Hong Kong Finance Professionals</span>
      <span class="lang-zh">為香港金融從業者而設</span>
    </p>
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white leading-tight mb-6">
      <span class="lang-en">Bridging Traditional Finance<br/>and <span class="text-cyan-400">Onchain Markets</span></span>
      <span class="lang-zh">傳統金融<span class="text-cyan-400">×</span><br/><span class="text-cyan-400">鏈上市場</span></span>
    </h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-zinc-400 max-w-3xl mb-12">
      <span class="lang-en">A practical guide to prediction markets, perpetual exchanges, and automated market making — for investment bankers, fund managers, family offices, and trading desks in Hong Kong.</span>
      <span class="lang-zh">涵蓋預測市場、永續合約交易所、自動化做市商的實用指南 — 為投資銀行、基金經理、家族辦公室及交易部門而設。</span>
    </p>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 mb-16">
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">$2.9B</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500 mt-1">
          <span class="lang-en">BlackRock BUIDL<br/>Tokenized Treasuries AUM</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">BlackRock BUIDL<br/>代幣化美債管理資產</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">$1.5T+</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500 mt-1">
          <span class="lang-en">JP Morgan Kinexys<br/>Total Transactions Processed</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">JP Morgan Kinexys<br/>已處理交易總額</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">HK$100億</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500 mt-1">
          <span class="lang-en">Hong Kong Government<br/>Tokenized Green Bond</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">香港政府<br/>代幣化綠色債券</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">$600M</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500 mt-1">
          <span class="lang-en">ICE (NYSE Parent)<br/>Investment in Polymarket</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">ICE（NYSE母公司）<br/>投資Polymarket</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-16">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">
      <span class="lang-en">Who Is This For</span>
      <span class="lang-zh">適合誰</span>
    </h2>
    <p class="text-zinc-500 mb-8">
      <span class="lang-en">Whether you're exploring these markets personally or evaluating them for your business, this guide provides the context you need.</span>
      <span class="lang-zh">無論你是個人探索還是為業務評估，本指南提供你所需的背景知識。</span>
    </p>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-4">
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="text-cyan-400 font-medium text-sm mb-2">
          <span class="lang-en">Investment Banking</span><span class="lang-zh">投資銀行</span>
        </p>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm">
          <span class="lang-en">ECM/DCM teams exploring tokenized issuance. Structured products moving onchain. New advisory opportunities.</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">ECM/DCM團隊探索代幣化發行。結構化產品上鏈。新的顧問業務機遇。</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="text-cyan-400 font-medium text-sm mb-2">
          <span class="lang-en">Asset Management</span><span class="lang-zh">資產管理</span>
        </p>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm">
          <span class="lang-en">Funds seeking onchain yield, new asset classes, and 24/7 market access. Tokenized treasuries as collateral.</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">基金尋求鏈上收益、新資產類別及24/7市場准入。代幣化美債可作為抵押品。</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="text-cyan-400 font-medium text-sm mb-2">
          <span class="lang-en">Family Offices</span><span class="lang-zh">家族辦公室</span>
        </p>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm">
          <span class="lang-en">52% of HK family offices plan crypto allocation. Digital assets now qualify for tax concessions.</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">52%的香港家族辦公室計劃配置加密資產。數字資產已納入稅務優惠範圍。</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="text-cyan-400 font-medium text-sm mb-2">
          <span class="lang-en">Prop Trading</span><span class="lang-zh">自營交易</span>
        </p>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm">
          <span class="lang-en">24/7 perpetual futures, pre-IPO exposure via HIP-3, onchain arbitrage, and funding rate strategies.</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">24/7永續合約、透過HIP-3參與Pre-IPO、鏈上套利及資金費率策略。</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="text-cyan-400 font-medium text-sm mb-2">
          <span class="lang-en">Compliance & Risk</span><span class="lang-zh">合規與風險</span>
        </p>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm">
          <span class="lang-en">Understanding DeFi products within the SFC framework. Preparing for upcoming VA dealer and custodian licensing.</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">在SFC框架下理解DeFi產品。為即將推出的虛擬資產經銷商及託管牌照做準備。</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-16">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">
      <span class="lang-en">Three Onchain Products to Understand</span>
      <span class="lang-zh">三個你需要了解的Onchain產品</span>
    </h2>
    <p class="text-zinc-500 mb-8">
      <span class="lang-en">Each represents a fundamental financial primitive — rebuilt on blockchain infrastructure.</span>
      <span class="lang-zh">每一個都是核心金融原語 — 在區塊鏈基礎設施上重建。</span>
    </p>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <a href={`${base}/products/polymarket`} class="group bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8 hover:border-cyan-800/50 transition-colors">
        <p class="text-sm text-cyan-400 font-medium mb-2">Prediction Market</p>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3 group-hover:text-cyan-400 transition-colors">Polymarket</h3>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm mb-4">
          <span class="lang-en">Trade on the outcome of real-world events. Binary contracts priced by market consensus. ICE (NYSE parent) invested $600M.</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">交易真實世界事件的結果。市場共識定價的二元合約。ICE（NYSE母公司）已投資$600M。</span>
        </p>
        <p class="text-zinc-600 text-sm">
          <span class="lang-en">30-day volume: $9.7B →</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">30日交易量：$9.7B →</span>
        </p>
      </a>
      <a href={`${base}/products/hyperliquid`} class="group bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8 hover:border-cyan-800/50 transition-colors">
        <p class="text-sm text-cyan-400 font-medium mb-2">Perpetual Exchange + Pre-IPO</p>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3 group-hover:text-cyan-400 transition-colors">Hyperliquid</h3>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm mb-4">
          <span class="lang-en">Crypto perpetual futures with up to 50x leverage. HIP-3 enables pre-IPO valuation exposure to SpaceX, OpenAI, Anthropic.</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">加密永續合約，最高50倍槓桿。HIP-3可交易SpaceX、OpenAI、Anthropic等Pre-IPO估值。</span>
        </p>
        <p class="text-zinc-600 text-sm">
          <span class="lang-en">Daily volume: $5-10B →</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">日交易量：$5-10B →</span>
        </p>
      </a>
      <a href={`${base}/products/amm`} class="group bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8 hover:border-cyan-800/50 transition-colors">
        <p class="text-sm text-cyan-400 font-medium mb-2">Automated Market Making</p>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3 group-hover:text-cyan-400 transition-colors">Onchain AMM</h3>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm mb-4">
          <span class="lang-en">Permissionless markets where anyone can trade, provide liquidity, or launch new tokens. No listing approval required.</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">無需許可的市場 — 任何人可交易、提供流動性或發行新代幣。無需上市審批。</span>
        </p>
        <p class="text-zinc-600 text-sm">
          <span class="lang-en">Uniswap daily volume: $1-2B →</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">Uniswap日交易量：$1-2B →</span>
        </p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-16">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-8">
      <span class="lang-en">Why Now</span>
      <span class="lang-zh">為什麼是現在</span>
    </h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8">
        <p class="text-cyan-400 font-medium mb-3">
          <span class="lang-en">Regulatory Clarity</span><span class="lang-zh">監管框架明確</span>
        </p>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm">
          <span class="lang-en">Hong Kong has licensed 12 virtual asset trading platforms, passed a stablecoin ordinance, and introduced tax concessions for family offices investing in digital assets.</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">香港已發出12個虛擬資產交易平台牌照、通過穩定幣條例，並為投資數字資產的家族辦公室推出稅務優惠。</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8">
        <p class="text-cyan-400 font-medium mb-3">
          <span class="lang-en">Institutional Adoption</span><span class="lang-zh">機構入場</span>
        </p>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm">
          <span class="lang-en">BlackRock, JP Morgan, Goldman Sachs, Citadel Securities, and the NYSE are all building onchain positions. This is infrastructure investment, not speculation.</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">BlackRock、JP Morgan、Goldman Sachs、Citadel Securities及NYSE均在建立鏈上佈局。這是基礎設施投資，不是投機。</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8">
        <p class="text-cyan-400 font-medium mb-3">
          <span class="lang-en">Infrastructure Maturity</span><span class="lang-zh">基礎設施成熟</span>
        </p>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm">
          <span class="lang-en">Sub-second settlement, $10B+ daily DEX volume, professional-grade tooling. The technology can now support serious capital.</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">亞秒級結算、日均DEX交易量超$10B、專業級工具。技術已可承載大規模資金運作。</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-16">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">
          <span class="lang-en">🌍 Global Moves</span><span class="lang-zh">🌍 全球動態</span>
        </h3>
        <div class="space-y-3 text-sm text-zinc-400">
          <p><span class="text-white font-medium">BlackRock</span> — BUIDL tokenized Treasuries, $2.9B AUM, 9 chains</p>
          <p><span class="text-white font-medium">JP Morgan</span> — Kinexys, $1.5T+ processed, onchain FX settlement</p>
          <p><span class="text-white font-medium">Goldman Sachs</span> — GS DAP, EIB €100M bond issuance onchain</p>
          <p><span class="text-white font-medium">Citadel Securities</span> — $200M into Kraken, crypto market-making</p>
          <p><span class="text-white font-medium">NYSE × Securitize</span> — 24/7 tokenized securities trading MOU</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">🇭🇰 Hong Kong</h3>
        <div class="space-y-3 text-sm text-zinc-400">
          <p><span class="text-white font-medium lang-en">HK Government</span><span class="text-white font-medium lang-zh">香港政府</span> — <span class="lang-en">Tokenized green bond HK$10B via HSBC Orion</span><span class="lang-zh">代幣化綠色債券HK$100億，經HSBC Orion結算</span></p>
          <p><span class="text-white font-medium">HSBC</span> — <span class="lang-en">Tokenized deposits live. Orion platform operational</span><span class="lang-zh">代幣化存款已上線。Orion平台運作中</span></p>
          <p><span class="text-white font-medium">Standard Chartered</span> — <span class="lang-en">First G-SIB spot crypto trading. HashKey banking partner</span><span class="lang-zh">首間全球系統重要性銀行提供現貨加密交易。HashKey銀行合作夥伴</span></p>
          <p><span class="text-white font-medium lang-en">Family Offices</span><span class="text-white font-medium lang-zh">家族辦公室</span> — <span class="lang-en">3,380+ in HK. 52% plan crypto allocation. Tax concessions available</span><span class="lang-zh">香港超過3,380間。52%計劃配置加密資產。稅務優惠已推出</span></p>
          <p><span class="text-white font-medium lang-en">12 Licensed VATPs</span><span class="text-white font-medium lang-zh">12間持牌VATP</span> — <span class="lang-en">HashKey & OSL leading, retail BTC/ETH access</span><span class="lang-zh">HashKey及OSL領頭，零售可買BTC/ETH</span></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-24">
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-green-950/30 to-zinc-900/50 border border-green-900/30 rounded-xl p-12 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
        <span class="lang-en">Questions? Let's Talk.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">有問題？歡迎聯繫。</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-400 mb-8">
        <span class="lang-en">Whether you're exploring these products for the first time or evaluating them for your business, we're happy to discuss.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">無論你是初次接觸這些產品，還是為業務進行評估，我們都樂意交流。</span>
      </p>
      <a href="https://wa.me/85256171671" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-8 py-4 bg-green-500 text-white font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-green-400 transition-colors">
        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 01-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 01-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 012.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0012.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 005.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.89-5.335 11.893-11.893a11.821 11.821 0 00-3.48-8.413z"/></svg>
        WhatsApp: +852 5617 1671
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
